These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, chess
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Hobby     | chess | dancing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Job    | analyst      | lawyer         |
| Sport   | skateboarding | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | cooking   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
