.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, april
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, writer
1. the writer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |
| Birthday   | april     | december   |
| Job        | firefighter | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-9::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, bike
2 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Transport   | bike | helicopter |
| Pet           | ferret    | mouse     |

